    {
      "id": "insight:a9007839a644d4d8",
      "properties": {
        "confidence": 0.7,
        "grounded": true,
        "text": "# Singletrack Sessions — Episode\n## Building Trails That Last\nHost: Maya\nGuest: Liam\nMaya: Welcome back to Singletrack Sessions.",
        "insight_type": "unknown",
        "position_hint": 0.5
      },
      "type": "Insight"
    },
    {
      "id": "insight:4fcccbf9181c2a25",
      "properties": {
        "confidence": 0.7,
        "grounded": true,
        "text": "Today we're talking about trail building, and I'm joined by Liam, trail builder for the Cascadia Alliance.",
        "insight_type": "unknown",
        "position_hint": 0.5
      },
      "type": "Insight"
    },
    {
      "id": "insight:f247d55c98c9b199",
      "properties": {
        "confidence": 0.7,
        "grounded": true,
        "text": "Excited for this one — trail building is something I've been thinking about a lot.",
        "insight_type": "unknown",
        "position_hint": 0.5
      },
      "type": "Insight"
    },
    {
      "id": "person:speaker-01",
      "properties": {
        "name": "Maya"
      },
      "type": "Person"
    },
    {
      "id": "quote:ef8d604714dd2892",
      "properties": {
        "char_end": 179,
        "char_start": 6,
        "episode_id": "5b39965f-22a2-54c9-9c42-e7a19d8da2da",
        "speaker_id": "person:speaker-01",
        "text": "Welcome back to Singletrack Sessions. Today we're talking about trail building, and I'm joined by Liam, trail builder for the Cascadia Alliance. Liam, thanks for being here.",
        "timestamp_end_ms": 6000,
        "timestamp_start_ms": 0,
        "transcript_ref": "transcripts/p01_e01.txt"
      },
      "type": "Quote"
    },
    {
      "id": "person:speaker-02",
      "properties": {
        "name": "Liam"
      },
      "type": "Person"
    },
    {
      "id": "quote:f6fc35aad65210f8",
      "properties": {
        "char_end": 282,
        "char_start": 186,
        "episode_id": "5b39965f-22a2-54c9-9c42-e7a19d8da2da",
        "speaker_id": "person:speaker-02",
        "text": "Thanks, Maya. Excited for this one — trail building is something I've been thinking about a lot.",
        "timestamp_end_ms": 12000,
        "timestamp_start_ms": 6000,
        "transcript_ref": "transcripts/p01_e01.txt"
      },
      "type": "Quote"
    },
    {
      "id": "quote:4f0af7a40ce52996",
      "properties": {
        "char_end": 483,
        "char_start": 289,
        "episode_id": "5b39965f-22a2-54c9-9c42-e7a19d8da2da",
        "speaker_id": "person:speaker-01",
        "text": "Before we dive in, a quick word from our sponsor Strava. Strava is the home for athletes — track every ride, run, and swim, and compare segments with friends. Use code POD for an extended trial.",
        "timestamp_end_ms": 18000,
        "timestamp_start_ms": 12000,
        "transcript_ref": "transcripts/p01_e01.txt"
      },
      "type": "Quote"
    },
    {
      "id": "quote:f344c76240322df1",
      "properties": {
        "char_end": 553,
        "char_start": 483,
        "episode_id": "5b39965f-22a2-54c9-9c42-e7a19d8da2da",
        "speaker_id": "person:speaker-01",
        "text": "Let's start there. What's the most underrated piece of trail building?",
        "timestamp_end_ms": 24000,
        "timestamp_start_ms": 18000,
        "transcript_ref": "transcripts/p01_e01.txt"
      },
      "type": "Quote"
    },
    {
      "id": "quote:7f2246720f0d0d71",
      "properties": {
        "char_end": 826,
        "char_start": 560,
        "episode_id": "5b39965f-22a2-54c9-9c42-e7a19d8da2da",
        "speaker_id": "person:speaker-02",
        "text": "The short answer is Drainage is the single highest-leverage design choice on any trail. If water leaves on its own, the trail will last a decade. We've seen this play out at teams using Spoke & Wrench. Once you internalize that, the rest of the decisions get easier.",
        "timestamp_end_ms": 30000,
        "timestamp_start_ms": 24000,
        "transcript_ref": "transcripts/p01_e01.txt"
      },
      "type": "Quote"
    },
    {
      "id": "quote:343efaa683fd96ac",
      "properties": {
        "char_end": 929,
        "char_start": 833,
        "episode_id": "5b39965f-22a2-54c9-9c42-e7a19d8da2da",
        "speaker_id": "person:speaker-01",
        "text": "Push back on the conventional wisdom for me. What's the most underrated piece of trail building?",
        "timestamp_end_ms": 36000,
        "timestamp_start_ms": 30000,
        "transcript_ref": "transcripts/p01_e01.txt"
      },
      "type": "Quote"
    }
